<Layout title="AIMS Travel" description="AIMS Travel — international group tour inspiration for cultural journeys to Africa, Asia, Europe, the Americas, and the Middle East. Small groups, deep immersion, amazing experiences.">

  <div class="hero-band">
    <h1>AIMS Travel</h1>
    <p>Aiming to Make Your Travel Amazing</p>
  </div>

  <main>

    <img src="/images/home-hero.png" class="dest-hero-img" alt="Cinematic international travel scene — golden light, adventure, discovery" />

    <h1>Discover the World with AIMS Travel</h1>
    <p>
      AIMS Travel was a premier international group tour operator offering meticulously planned cultural journeys to the world's most compelling destinations. From the wildlife-rich plains of East Africa to the ancient temples of Asia, the imperial capitals of Europe to the lost cities of the Americas — AIMS Travel curated experiences that combined expert local guides, exceptional accommodations, and the camaraderie of like-minded travelers.
    </p>

    <div class="dest-grid">
      <a href="/destinations/africa" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Africa</h3>
        <p>South Africa, Kenya &amp; Tanzania Safari, Botswana, Namibia</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/asia" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Asia &amp; the Orient</h3>
        <p>China &amp; Yangtze River, India, Vietnam &amp; Cambodia, Thailand</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/europe" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Europe</h3>
        <p>Greece, Central Europe, Russia, Scandinavia, Sicily, Italy</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/americas" class="dest-card">
        <h3>The Americas</h3>
        <p>Peru &amp; Machu Picchu, Ecuador &amp; Galapagos, Costa Rica, Cuba</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations/middle-east" class="dest-card">
        <h3>Middle East</h3>
        <p>Egypt &amp; the Nile, Turkey, Israel</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/destinations" class="dest-card">
        <h3>All Destinations</h3>
        <p>Browse the complete catalog of international tour programs</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>The AIMS Travel Experience</h3>
      <p>
        AIMS Travel built its reputation on small group sizes, hand-selected local guides, and itineraries that went beyond the typical tourist circuit. Every tour was designed to provide genuine cultural immersion — staying in locally-owned properties, dining with local families, and visiting sites rarely seen by independent travelers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Why Travelers Chose AIMS</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Expert local guides</strong> with deep regional knowledge</li>
      <li><strong>Small group departures</strong> — typically 16–24 travelers</li>
      <li><strong>All-inclusive pricing</strong> — flights, hotels, guides, most meals</li>
      <li><strong>Custom tour programs</strong> for special interest groups</li>
      <li><strong>Decades of experience</strong> operating international itineraries</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-top:2rem"><a href="/destinations">Explore all destinations &rarr;</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/about">About AIMS Travel &rarr;</a></p>
  </main>
